todotxt.el mode by AdolfoVillafiorita is a major mode for editing todo.txt files.

* See http://todotxt.com for details about this format.

It supports an extension to the default format to manage due dates and recurring tasks. 

Available from: 

* https://github.com/avillafiorita/todotxt-mode

In order to automatically use this mode when editing todo.txt files, you can use this code for your init.el file:

    (require 'todotxt)
    (add-to-list 'auto-mode-alist '("\\todo.txt\\'" . todotxt-mode))

